&lt;p&gt;首先将RGB图像转成灰度值（下图左）&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;code&gt;grayScale = ( (0.3 * R) + (0.59 * G) + (0.11 * B) )
